00:46:35,180 --> 00:46:37,100
Tell me the truth.
Just tell me what happened?

645
00:46:37,600 --> 00:46:39,600
Romesh, please.
This isn't your problem.

646
00:46:39,720 --> 00:46:42,310
This is my problem.
This is my problem.

647
00:46:42,520 --> 00:46:44,640
