"It engulfs my heart."

675
00:48:31,140 --> 00:48:37,060
"Your absence makes
me cry inconsolably."

676
00:48:37,180 --> 00:48:43,270
"Why aren't you like your reflection?"

677
00:48:43,520 --> 00:48:49,970
"Why isn't your
disposition like your face?"

