Hello, doctor.

1606
01:59:30,140 --> 01:59:33,680
Aren't you the same
doctor that's on TV..

1607
01:59:35,180 --> 01:59:36,720
I am God!

1608
01:59:37,970 --> 01:59:40,270
I pulled thousands of
