1621
02:00:09,140 --> 02:00:11,470
So, if he's God then
I am a bloody doctor!

1622
02:00:12,220 --> 02:00:13,390
Doctor?
- Not now, later.

1623
02:00:14,020 --> 02:00:15,600
Just two minutes.
- Please go.

1624
02:00:20,560 --> 02:00:24,520
I am as powerful as
your so called God.

1625
02:00:26,850 --> 02:00:28,520
Hello.
- Dr. Asthana speaking.

1626
02:00:28,640 --> 02:00:30,060
Give the phone to your sir.
- Yes, sir.

1627
02:00:31,310 --> 02:00:33,890
Sir. Dr. Asthana.

1628
02:00:37,680 --> 02:00:40,220
Sir's in the bathroom.
- No need to say anything.

1629
02:00:40,930 --> 02:00:42,470
Tell him I've understood everything.

1630
02:00:43,020 --> 02:00:44,140
Coward!

1631
02:00:46,390 --> 02:00:47,600
Get out of the way.

1632
02:01:03,890 --> 02:01:05,430
Dr. Asthana, we've a
warrant against you.

1633
02:01:18,140 --> 02:01:19,930
Dr. Riya will please stand.

1634
02:01:24,020 --> 02:01:27,140
Dr. Riya has broken her
oath taken in the court.

1635
