Lied to the court.

1636
02:01:29,430 --> 02:01:33,180
That was just a way
to expose the truth.

1637
02:01:33,680 --> 02:01:36,100
The court respects her intentions.

1638
02:01:36,970 --> 02:01:40,390
Since she swore in the court of law..

1639
02:01:41,100 --> 02:01:44,770
..the court fines her Rs.20,000.

1640
02:01:49,140 --> 02:01:51,430
Shekhawat Hospital is
guilty of negligence..

1641
02:01:51,560 --> 02:01:53,020
..beyond reasonable doubt.

1642
02:01:53,310 --> 02:01:55,390
And the court, on this day..

1643
02:01:55,520 --> 02:01:58,350
..12th December, 2012..

1644
02:01:58,720 --> 02:02:00,850
..orders Shekhawat Hospital..

1645
02:02:01,270 --> 02:02:05,520
..to pay a compensation of Rs.10
crores to Ankur Arora's mother..

1646
02:02:05,640 --> 02:02:07,560
..within the next 15 days.

1647
02:02:10,180 --> 02:02:12,890
And, the court finds Dr.
Asthana guilty..

1648
02:02:13,020 --> 02:02:14,970
..for Ankur Arora's death.

1649
02:02:15,100 --> 02:02:17,310
And sentences him to
three years of imprisonment..

1650
02:02:17,430 --> 02:02:19,270
..under section 304.

1651
02:02:19,350 --> 02:02:20,680
The court is dismissed.

1652
