1655
02:02:39,770 --> 02:02:46,020
"You don't have any memory of me."

1656
02:02:46,390 --> 02:02:49,520
"Life, better mend your ways."

1657
02:02:49,640 --> 02:02:52,600
"Better change for the good."

1658
02:02:52,890 --> 02:02:55,560
"Have pity, don't be so harsh."

1659
02:02:55,680 --> 02:02:59,310
"Don't be so stubborn."

1660
02:02:59,390 --> 02:03:02,270
"Why do people change?"

1661
02:03:02,350 --> 02:03:05,520
"Why aren't they always with us?"

1662
02:03:05,640 --> 02:03:11,770
"Life, you're jealous of my dreams."

1663
02:03:11,890 --> 02:03:17,600
"Why aren't you like your image?"

1664
02:03:18,020 --> 02:03:25,350
"Why aren't you like
what you seem to be?"

1665
02:04:02,970 --> 02:04:08,810
"You've so many complaints with me."

1666
02:04:09,220 --> 02:04:15,310
"Our love's lost in these distances."

1667
02:04:15,600 --> 02:04:22,020
"I've been living by the moment."

1668
02:04:22,140 --> 02:04:28,390
"Why does life has
so many complaints?"

1669
02:04:28,850 --> 02:04:31,890
"You keep reminding us."

1670
02:04:32,020 --> 02:04:35,100
"Reminding us every moment."

1671
02:04:35,220 --> 02:04:41,430
"Brings us close to you."

1672
