"Life, you're jealous of my dreams."

1675
02:04:54,520 --> 02:04:57,560
"What's this void?"

1676
02:04:57,680 --> 02:05:00,850
"It torments the heart."

1677
02:05:00,970 --> 02:05:06,850
"And makes the heart weep."

1678
